    "description": {
      "value": "<p>The chakra bullet you fire erupts underground, creating a giant explosion of fire underneath targets. Select a 10-foot radius within the range. All creatures in the space must make a dexterity saving throw. On a failed save they take 7d8+6 Fire damage. On a success they take half. If a creature fails this save by 5 or more, they take twice the result in damage.</p><p><strong>At Higher Ranks:</strong> For each rank you cast this jutsu above B-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3 and the damage by 2d8+1.</p>",
